 \"the Track\" because the dance floor was so long and thin.","Fact9":"It use to cost 30-85 cents a person to get into the Savoy. That'd be $6-16 today!","Got It":"Got It","How to Play":"How to Play","Intro":"\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0d82 \u0db1\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0ddd\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db6\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd6\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0db8\u0dda \u0db8\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dda \u0d94\u0db6\u0dda \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dad\u0dcf \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1!","MobileTutorial1":"Hold or place your device between one another.","MobileTutorial2":"Tap the buttons in time with the note.","Mute":"Mute","New Game":"New Game","Next":"Next","One Player":"One Player","Pause":"Pause","Paused":"Paused","PostmodernJukebox":"Postmodern Jukebox","Replay":"Replay","Resume":"Resume","Retry":"Retry","Score":"Score: {{}}","Search":"Search","Share Facebook":"Share on Facebook","Share Twitter":"Share on Twitter","Share1":"Share","Share2":"Link copied","ShareText":"Lindy Hop over to the dance floor and put your rhythm to the test in today's multiplayer #GoogleDoodle game celebrating swing dancing and the Savoy Ballroom! ","Skip scene/tutorial":"Skip","Song1":"Let's Call the Whole Thing Off","Song2":"Solid As A Rock","Song3":"Bei Mir Bist Du Schoen","SongBonus":"Careless Whisper","Start":"Start","Start Over":"Start Over","Swap":"\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1","Title":"Celebrating Swing Dancing and the Savoy Ballroom!","Two Players":"Two Players","Unmute":"Unmute"}